OL,7,FTwo of the urns were inscribed with
OL,8,Fnames - Hispana and Senicio - but the
OL,9,Fidentities of the other two men and
OL,10,Ftwo women are not known.
OL,12,F"At first, it surprised us that the
OL,13,Fliquid was preserved in the funeral
OL,14,Furn," said Juan Manuel Roman,
OL,15,FCarmona's town archeologist.
